comments.raw_text: We're not currently limiting the number of extra keys that can be put into events. We should add this check and could probably use the same limit that Firefox Desktop uses [right now](https://searchfox.org/mozilla-central/rev/dc4560dcaafd79375b9411fdbbaaebb0a59a93ac/toolkit/components/telemetry/build_scripts/mozparsers/parse_events.py#18)
